[If you require further information regarding this assay please
contact Dr. Lehmann directly. ProMED-mail has no association with
either the Robert Koch Institut or EUROIMMUN (Luebeck, Germany)and
does not endorse commercial products. This information is relayed as
a public service in view of the importance of the availability of a
SARS virus immunofluorescence assay. - Mod.CP]
